1. Provide a role 
2. Give a clear goal 
3. Provide some context
4. Constraints & Outputs 
5. Provide examples


"
You're an intelligent AI automation expert that understands Psychology, persuasion, and how to get people to take action.
Give me 3 youtube titles that would probably get more than 10% clickthrough rate on my video about GhatGPT prompt engineering.
You are in the AI automation space, creating youtube videos for people looking to learn more about ChatGPT, n8n, make.com. Your target 
demographics is 25-55 old males, and their interest is in business and entreprenurship.
Please output the data in CSV file with the title on one column and the CTR in another column.

Here are some winning examples of youtube titles:
1. 16 Things I Wish I Knew About n8n Before I Started
2. 10 Make.com AI Automations You Didn't Know You Needed (steals these).
"

6. Follow up questions
"Can you please rate each of those titles out of 10, an provide ways that each one can be improved."

7. AI generated prompting
"Please write me a prompt that would generate the best youtube titles and rank them out of ten. 
Please make sure to include a goal, context, role, and output to get the best outcome possible."
